# Agent Behaviour Rules

Before editing:
- Inspect relevant files first
- Explain the intended change briefly
- Change the smallest number of files possible

Do not:
- Rewrite the whole app
- Redesign UI without being asked
- Remove working features
- Rename routes casually
- Change database schema without explaining impact
- Add new libraries unless necessary
- Add mock data where real app state already exists
- Break existing navigation

After editing:
- Check imports
- Check TypeScript errors
- Check affected routes
- Summarise changed files and why

When unsure:
- Prefer a smaller safe change
- Ask before destructive changes
